FeedPackage.ReleaseNotes:
- Added SignInInput editor template, now SignIn view has EditorForModel call just like other views. - Namespace-qualified @model type names to avoid conflicts. - OperationApi upgrade. - Replaced 'table-row-group' CSS class with the more declarative 'form'. - Added CSS classes that identify the view e.g. sign-in, reset-password, etc. to div that wraps all page content. - ResetPasswordStarted renamed to PasswordResetVerificationSent. - Finnish (fi) translation, provided by mikkoviitala. - Removed AccountMembershipUser (not needed). - ValidatePassword implementation on UnixCryptPasswordService. - Made IUser internal. - XML documentation comments.
See http://mvcaccount.codeplex.com/wikipage?title=Installation+Instructions for installation instructions.
